  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <pb facs="5"/>
   <lg>
      <l>COme Drunkennesse, vntrusse,</l>
      <l>and naked strip thee:</l>
      <l>For without mercy</l>
      <l>I will soundly whip thee.</l>
      <l>I haue prepar'd a Scourge</l>
      <l>I hope will smart,</l>
      <l>Because I doe abhorre thee</l>
      <l>with my heart.</l>
      <l>Then will I pinch, nip, seare,</l>
      <l>and brand thy skinne,</l>
      <l>To make thee (if thou canst)</l>
      <l>to feele thy sinne.</l>
      <l>So serue thee in thy kinde,</l>
      <l>and let thee passe,</l>
      <l>For the most vildest Rogue</l>
      <l>that euer was.</l>
      <l>Ile vse thee like a Dogge, a Iew, a Slaue.</l>
      <l>Expect no mercy from my hands to haue.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
